title: Where is my Alpha Client Summoner icon?
body: I had the alpha client, but I haven't received the free Summoner icon for testers? Where is mine? D:

replies.body:
We're still sending these out until the end of the month. If you don't see it by then, let us know in a [support ticket.](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new)

Let me know if you have any questions!
